CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is manually populated. This field is used to automatically select which risk grade template should be used as the template for a risk rating review during creation. To use this field, you can set the value which has to be entered or selected from the field in "LLC_BI__Template_Object_Field_Name__c" for this particular Risk Grade Template to be used during the creation of a Risk Rating Review.
CustomField.label: Template Object Field Value
